bsp;</p><p>If you have a question please call ________</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you feel you should have access, please email cclwww@rit.edu and we&#39;ll set you right up! </p>','2010-09-03 13:25:51','cclwww','clubs','fairAdminDeny','Access Denied'),(97,0,'  <p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><br /><img src=\"/main/uploads/owl.jpg\" alt=\"owl\" title=\"owl\" width=\"94\" height=\"94\" /></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>\\</p><p>Changeddddddsdsgsfg</p><p>Hey lady--you&#39;ve got the love I need </p><p>&nbsp;<img src=\"/main/uploads/baby-polar-bear.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"469\" height=\"140\" /></p><p> Maybe, more than enough. <br /> Oh Darling Darling Darling, walk a while with me <br /> Oh you&#39;ve got so much... <br /> <br /> Many times I&#39;ve loved - Many times been bitten <br /> Many times I&#39;ve gazed along the open road. <br /> <br /> Many times I&#39;ve lied - Many times I&#39;ve listened <br /> Many times I&#39;ve wondered how much there is to know. <br /> <br /> Many dreams come true and some have silver linings <br /> I live for my dream and a pocketful of gold. <br /> <br /> Mellow is the man who knows what he&#39;s been missing <br /><a href=\"http://www.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\"> Many many men can&#39;t see the open road. </a><br /> <br /> Many is a word that only leaves you guessing <br /> Guessing &#39;bout a thing you really ought to know, ooh! <br /> You really ought to know...</p>Edited by solo','2010-09-16 20:11:32','cclwww','about','awesome','Over the Hills and Far Away'),(98,0,'<h3 style=\"color: black; font-size: 15px\">8th Annual Club Fair Organization Registration Form</h3> <p> <strong>Event Date:</strong>&nbsp;Sunday, September 5, 2010<br /> <strong>Event Time:</strong>&nbsp;1:00 &lt;96&gt; 4:00 pm<br /> <strong>Location:</strong>&nbsp;Gordon Field House and Activities Center </p>  <p> This event is for first-year and transfer students and will conclude the week-long New Student Orientation program.  This is a great opportunity for your group to get new students interested in, and involved with, your organizations. </p>  <ul> <li>Set up begins at Noon.</li> <li>All tables must be staffed exclusively by students of the organization.</li> <li>Each organization will receive 1 table and 2 chairs with your registration.</li> <li>Power is available to groups who request it on this form.</li> </ul>  <p> <strong>Instructions</strong><br /> Please fill out the information below.  Make sure to check Power Source if you will need power for your display.  If you do not check yes, your organization will not receive power.  Indicate any other special requests in the space provided.  Staff will make every effort to accommodate special requests, but cannot guarantee all requests. </p>  <p> <strong>Questions?</strong><br /> Contact Alvin Roberts at ajrccl@rit.edu</p><h1><a href=\"/main/clubs/fairRequest\">&nbsp;All Set? Click here to Register&nbsp;</a></h1><p><a href=\"/main/clubs/fairAdmin\">admin </a></p> ','2010-09-13 11:20:26','mas1042','clubs','fair','Clubs Fair Info'),(102,0,'Rick is our awesome opossom. Unfortunatlly he was eaten by a polar bear. Here is a <a href=\"http://duckmylife.com\">picture</a> of it.<img src=\"/main/uploads/1baby-polar-bear.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"92\" height=\"226\" />','2010-09-16 13:20:49','cclwww','about','rick','Ricks page'),(101,0,'Hi, If you have ended up here, you are not where you inteded!','2010-09-15 13:43:35','cclwww','uploads','index','Bot Catcher');
